title: Dean Yeagle - Scribblings
description:
Format: PDF
Genre: Sketchbook
Published: N/A

Book Description: Regularly published in Playboy magazine, Yeagle has spent most of his career in animation, working on television ads and feature films. He's also illustrated children's books and magazines, and recently done work for Astonish Comics. This collection demonstrates Dean's mastery of animation style, humor, and ladies, as well as his ability to show character in every face.
These sketches, preliminary drawings, roughs and doodles cover a range of styles and character types, and have incredible vitality. Here are pinup girls, puppies, twerps, varmints, frogs, mugs, gargoyles, squirrels, fish, swine, geezers, dragons, and Mandy.
